{"tid":1939598,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【撐警星】張智霖赴無罩宴後首現身 認防疫意識唔夠：事件過咗去","createTime":"2020-03-23T08:32:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T08:38:37.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"50b6117b3518e5218290ef45de1fd4cb571526ed","tid":1939598,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T08:32:43.000Z","msg":"張智霖（Chilam）與警務處處長鄧炳強、警務處人事部遴選委員會總警司謝振中等高級警務人員，今年2月於又一村俱樂部出席「撐警無罩宴」，歌舞昇平，同場有成龍、曾志偉與譚詠麟等一眾香港巨星。<br />\n<br />\n聚餐後Chilam首次現身，今天於銅鑼灣出席保良局捐贈口罩活動，並獲委任為保良親善大使，Chilam謂希望能夠幫助老中青不同的年齡層：「今次係第2次做保良大使，好榮幸，希望可以幫助唔同年齡層，小朋友要愛護、年青人要溝通、老人家要關懷，希望身體力行，令社會更加融洽。」Chilam更謂已訂購4萬口罩，捐贈有需要的人，包括上班族、學習障礙的小朋友，他說：「我係會一路去做，直至疫情完結。」<br />\n<br />\n警星餐敍後被網民瘋狂洗版，今天Chilam被問到心情有否受到影響？Chilam說：「冇嘅&hellip;&hellip;都係&hellip;&hellip;都唔識講。」至於太太袁詠儀也被洗版式狂轟，是否感到不快？他則說：「唔回應嘞，事件過咗去，大家向前看，希望香港大家一條心去抗疫，呢個係比任何事情更重要。」問到飯局的照片中各人均沒有戴口罩，Chilam說：「可能係食飯（冇戴），食完飯都戴返，不過防疫意識係冇咁敏感，都係啱嘅。」<br />\n<br />\nChilam又透露囝囝魔童也知道發生何事，卻沒感到不快。至於任保良大使，是否希望洗底？Chilam說：「其實係機緣巧合下做大使，自己亦冇任何計劃會去做啲乜嘢。」<br />\n<br />\n另外，武漢肺炎疫情嚴峻，Chilam透露早前一家到布吉曬曬太陽，現時盡量留在家中避炎，同時要跟兒子一同網上學習，他笑言並不容易，令他在這方面的知識進步了。而Chilam指有家人在澳洲，他不時會留意當地情況，希望大家都不要恐慌及搶購物資。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200323/large/1584946274_f79b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200323%2Flarge%2F1584946274_f79b.jpg&h=e85f3ae7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200323/large/1584946584_59a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200323%2Flarge%2F1584946584_59a0.jpg&h=04d61d48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200323/DNTMGGE4TD7SDU7F45YENPJJFM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200323%2FDNTMGGE4TD7SDU7F45YENPJJFM%2F&d=Eps995EZp4R4ibMzYmnfr35V8GO7j56WmnfPW9WRM38%3D&h=f0d0367a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200323%2FDNTMGGE4TD7SDU7F45YENPJJFM%2F&h=55b40cf1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200323/DNTMGGE4TD7SDU7F45YENPJJFM/</a><br />\n<br />\n條友想當冇事發生，佢就想啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ad057924367dbbea56459668fee54ad41545ea","tid":1939598,"uid":114072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T08:33:39.000Z","msg":"過乜撚咗去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e88d8a3fe02f01c90f909dd67dbf4ad54b56c80","tid":1939598,"uid":227597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T08:38:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}